    "data": [
        [
            [
                "[color=#ffff00]How to play:[/color]\n    - Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to go to the next dialogue\n    - Press [color=#ffff00]Arrows Up/Down[/color] to select an option when available"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You are an up and coming merc trying to make it big in Night City. You’ve taken gigs in the past on your own, but they caught little attention. Your most recent gig did catch someone's attention though. A Fixer named “Faraday”.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]He says he liked how fast and clean you were able to finish the job and would like to offer some more gigs. You’ve never worked with any fixers before and you’ve never heard of this Fixer before. [/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]The fixers terms are a 50/50 split of profits, but they have a long list of gigs so there will always be work. The fixer says if you would like to accept his terms, meet him at the “Afterlife” bar at 10:00 PM.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You don’t like the 50/50 split and feel you won’t make much money working with the fixer, but they will always provide gigs.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Working on your own would gain you more profits, but finding gigs is hard without a fixer and you might not have any stable income. Would you like to meet with the Fixer or find your own gigs?[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Though you will make less money, you decide to meet with Faraday. At the Afterlife, you spot Faraday in a private booth and walk over to speak with him.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]As you approach the booth, you see he is talking to a different client. Faraday sees you approach and signals you to wait till they are done with their conversation.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You lean against the wall on your phone and wait for the conversation to end. You hear mumbles of the conversation but can’t make out anything that they are saying.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You lean in a little closer to the booth and can hear them say “if you find the stash before Arasaka does, you can take all the goods. I don’t usually offer this to my clients, but you’ve…”.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Maybe snooping in might not be the best decision, so you lean away from the booth and continue to wait till the conversation is done.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]After what feels like forever, the client walks out of the booth and you hear Faraday call out your name. You walk into the booth and sit down. Faraday doesn’t greet you. All he says is…[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[color=#ffff00][b]Faraday:[/b][/color] Here is the contract. This contract is final and non-negotiable."
            ],
            [
                "[i]Faraday slides the tablet with the contract to you. You briefly look over his terms until a line catches your eye. There is a 50/50 split with all income, including any extra money found on the job. [/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You notice Faraday starts glaring at you as you continue to read. You feel pressured to make a decision soon and you don’t finish reading the contract all the way.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[color=#ffff00][b]Faraday:[/b][/color] Your first gig starts now. I have sent the coordinates to your phone. You have 3 hours effective now to complete this task. There will be [b]NO MISTAKES[/b]. I will not clean up your mess."
            ],
            [
                "[i]You find the coordinates Faraday sent to you on your phone and immediately head to the gig. As you are heading to the gig, you realize Faraday never told you what kind of gig this is.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You message Faraday for information about the gig but before you could even hit send, Faraday send the details of the gig to you.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You sit there wondering if it was just good timing or maybe Faraday is watching every move you make. A chill runs down your spine as you think about being under constant surveillance.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Once you get to the coordinates, you start looking for the car to repo. As you walk around the house, the car is nowhere to be found.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You see the garage has a window on the garage door and peak inside. Your eyes catch sight of the car, but so does the owner of the car. Before you can even react, you hear a loud [b]BANG[/b].[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Everything fades to black, and you are met with a message that says “Flatlined”.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to restart..."
            ],
            [
                "[i]You decide meeting with Faraday is not worth it and decide to find your own gigs. You begin looking for gigs immediately.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]After a couple of days, you haven’t found a single gig yet. You are now starting to regret not meeting up with Faraday. You still have enough money to get to the end of the month, but you are really starting to get worried.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "- - - - - Next Month - - - - -"
            ],
            [
                "[i]It is now the end of the month and you didn’t find a single gig. Your landlord comes to your apartment and evicts you for missed rent payments.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You try contacting Faraday again now desperate for money, but you are met with a message that says “The number you are trying to reach is unavailable. This number wither no longer exists or you are blocked”.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to restart..."
            ],
            [
                "[i]You decide the risk is worth it and lean in even closer to snoop on the conversation.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You hear Faraday say “The coordinates are…”. Right as he is about to finish what he is saying, a bartender approaches the booth and startles you. You fall over right in front of the booth.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]As you look up from the floor, your eyes lock with Faraday. He realizes you have been snooping in on the conversation. He then says to the client in the booth,[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[color=#ffff00][b]Faraday:[/b][/color] How about one more quick clean up gig? I will even throw in a bonus if you do it now."
            ],
            [
                "[i]The client gets up and approaches towards you. You realize what a clean up gig is as the client takes you outside the bar.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You try to break free away from him, but his grip is too strong. He pushes you to the ground behind the bar and before you can even catch yourself, you hear a loud [b]BANG[/b].[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Everything fades to black and you are met with a message that states “Flatlined”.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to restart..."
            ],
            [
                "[color=#ffff00][b]Faraday:[/b][/color] You are just wasting me time and money. I have no use for you."
            ],
            [
                "[i]After declining the contract, you leave the booth and walk out of the bar.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You sit there lost wondering what to do now. You ask yourself, “Should I have given more thought on the contract before declining?\"[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]You are now back to square one with no gigs or jobs to do.[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "[i]Maybe you should’ve just signed the contract…[/i]"
            ],
            [
                "Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to restart..."
            ]
